HUGE things on the way!!! (Just as my psychics told me hahaha 😝) I’m so excited to announce that I am now a franchisee and have completed a franchise deal with Glo30, the doctor-led, subscription-based skincare studio!!! I’ve been a @glo30skincare member for over 10 years and am so excited to introduce Glo30 to Columbia, MD and surrounding areas. Thank you to Glo30’s incredibly brilliant and fearless founder and leader, @drarleenlamba , for believing in me and trusting me to carry on Glo30’s vision across Maryland. This is just the beginning 🙌🏽🙌🏽

SIDENOTE: This photo was taken at Glo30’s newest location at the Amazon HQ building in Arlington, VA. This is not my location. I’m still scouting spaces and look forward to sharing my journey with you. 😊

About GLO30:
Founded in 2012 by Dr. Arleen Lamba, GLO30 is a membership-based skincare company focused on providing personalized routine treatments, medical-grade products and high-tech, high-touch guidance – every 30 days. GLO30 has defined a new category in the skincare services space, bridging the gap between luxurious day spas and more invasive medical clinics and med spas. The service-based skincare franchise is an affordable, accessible and approachable middle ground that delivers customized care in an hour or less – every 30 days. Trained specialists and propriety technology consistently deliver treatments tailored to the unique skin needs and goals of every member. GLO30 currently operates four corporate locations, and is set to open the Amazon HQ2 in Arlington, VA in summer 2023. For more information, visit www.GLO30.com.

Go Corey! I’m so excited for his first high school basketball season. I can’t tell you how many times this boy had me at the Orthopedic Dr., X-Ray, MRI, physical therapists and trainers over the past two years. It’s been quite a frustrating journey and lesson in patience (most definitely more so for me lol, Corey never complained once).

But tonight, I was an extremely proud mom as I watched him get a double-double in his first HS basketball game as a freshman on varsity (against his dad’s alma mater). 🥰🥰🥰🙌🏽🙌🏽🙌🏽 I think his team is going to make some noise around here and I’m happy to cheer them on! I pray Corey and all of his teammates have a successful season and stay healthy and injury free. 🙏🏽

Primark is the perfect place to do a little bestie shopping! @gizellebryant and I had a blast visiting @Primark.USA at Arundel Mills in MD and stocked up on great quality, affordable goodies for ourselves and our loved ones. I can’t tell you how lucky I am to have a Primark near me! Did you know there are now 24 Primarks across the United States? And counting…! There is definitely a lot to take in here, so I’ll be back soon.

Oh, be sure to head over to Gizelle’s page to see the rest of her cute outfits and goodies!
